19namespace ZXing {
20namespace Pdf417 {
21
22/**
23* @author Guenther Grau
24*/
25class Codeword
26{
27 static const int BARCODE_ROW_UNKNOWN = -1;
28
29 int _startX = 0;
30 int _endX = 0;
31 int _bucket = 0;
32 int _value = 0;
33 int _rowNumber = BARCODE_ROW_UNKNOWN;
34
35public:
36 Codeword() {}
37 Codeword(int startX, int endX, int bucket, int value) : _startX(startX), _endX(endX), _bucket(bucket), _value(value) {}
38
39 bool hasValidRowNumber() const {
40 return isValidRowNumber(_rowNumber);
41 }
42
43 bool isValidRowNumber(int rowNumber) const {
44 return rowNumber != BARCODE_ROW_UNKNOWN && _bucket == (rowNumber % 3) * 3;
45 }
46
47 void setRowNumberAsRowIndicatorColumn() {
48 _rowNumber = (_value / 30) * 3 + _bucket / 3;
49 }
50
51 int width() const {
52 return _endX - _startX;
53 }
54
55 int startX() const {
56 return _startX;
57 }
58
59 int endX() const {
60 return _endX;
61 }
62
63 int bucket() const {
64 return _bucket;
65 }
66
67 int value() const {
68 return _value;
69 }
70
71 int rowNumber() const {
72 return _rowNumber;
73 }
74
75 void setRowNumber(int rowNumber) {
76 _rowNumber = rowNumber;
77 }
78};
79
80} // Pdf417
81} // ZXing
